---
import { C, FONT } from "../infographicTokens";
---

<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 720 300" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
  <title>Why oversizing hurts an inverter mini split</title>
  <desc>
    A right-sized inverter mini split modulates and runs long, steady, efficient cycles that dehumidify
    well. An oversized one can't turn down far enough, so it short cycles, controls humidity poorly, and
    loses the efficiency that makes inverters worthwhile.
  </desc>

  <rect x="8" y="8" width="704" height="284" rx="12" fill={C.panelBg} stroke={C.border} />
  <text x="24" y="36" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="14" font-weight="700">Oversizing defeats an inverter</text>
  <text x="24" y="56" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="11">Inverters earn their keep by modulating — too big and they can't turn down</text>

  <!-- Right-sized -->
  <rect x="24" y="76" width="320" height="200" rx="10" fill={C.greenLight} stroke={C.green} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="40" y="100" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="13" font-weight="700">Right-sized</text>
  <!-- steady wave -->
  <path d="M40 150 Q 80 130 120 150 T 200 150 T 280 150 T 320 150" fill="none" stroke={C.green} stroke-width="2.5" />
  <text x="40" y="196" fill={C.green} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">+ Long, steady, modulating cycles</text>
  <text x="40" y="218" fill={C.green} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">+ Strong humidity control</text>
  <text x="40" y="240" fill={C.green} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">+ Hits the rated efficiency</text>
  <text x="40" y="262" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="10">Quiet, even comfort at part load</text>

  <!-- Oversized -->
  <rect x="376" y="76" width="320" height="200" rx="10" fill={C.redLight} stroke={C.red} stroke-width="1.5" />
  <text x="392" y="100" fill={C.dark} font-family={FONT} font-size="13" font-weight="700">Oversized</text>
  <!-- spiky on/off -->
  <path d="M392 170 L392 130 L430 130 L430 170 L470 170 L470 130 L508 130 L508 170 L548 170 L548 135 L586 135 L586 170" fill="none" stroke={C.red} stroke-width="2.5" />
  <text x="392" y="196" fill={C.red} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">− Short cycles on and off</text>
  <text x="392" y="218" fill={C.red} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">− Leaves the room cold but clammy</text>
  <text x="392" y="240" fill={C.red} font-family={FONT} font-size="11" font-weight="700">− Loses inverter efficiency</text>
  <text x="392" y="262" fill={C.muted} font-family={FONT} font-size="10">More wear, more noise, higher bills</text>
</svg>
